{"id":293505,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-北京李方平等人举牌抗议多名律师遭殴打/","date":"2013-05-14T16:00:42Z","modified":"2013-05-14T16:00:42Z","title":"维权网 | 北京李方平等人举牌抗议多名律师遭殴打的严重侵权行为","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员华新报道）四川省资阳迎接镇二娥湖有一家度假中心，名为度假山庄，实质是黑监狱，专门对无辜公民洗脑的法制教育中心。当地警方经常将无辜公民非法绑架到此，限制公民人身自由，有的公民被长期关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>年之久。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在获知资阳黑监狱的非法迫害公民真相后，北京江天勇、唐吉田、梁小军、蔺其磊、郭海跃、张科科、唐天昊等律师，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日上午</span><span>到达资阳市迎接镇二娥湖黑监狱进行围观监督，但是不久多位律师便遭到有关人员暴力殴打，江天勇律师腿部、唐天昊头部均被殴打致伤。随后多名律师被以“扰乱公务”控制关押在派出所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当天下午李和平、王成、温海波、杨慧文前往事发地的派出所报案救援，结果也被控制关押，直到次日（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日）上午十点，十几位律师才陆续获释。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日中午，北京律师滕彪、李方平、肖国珍、刘巍等得知众律师被暴力殴打后，纷纷谴责当局的侵权行为，并举出“资阳：狂殴律师掩盖不了洗脑班的罪恶！”等抗议标语。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>对于资阳暴力殴打关押众律师的侵权行为，李方平律师表示强烈谴责。他说江天勇等人本身是律师也是公民，作为公民有权利对正在发生的犯罪行为进行监督，而作为资阳市的有关执法部门不去调查犯罪嫌疑人，反而对公民的合法监督加以迫害殴打，更是罪上加罪的违法侵害行为。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-RY5ImNDIgOc/UZJPM9yUvoI/AAAAAAAAh-c/4wo8jxeefIM/s1600/59793E7D-B617-486C-83FF-A91EA529C091_w640_r1_s.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-RY5ImNDIgOc/UZJPM9yUvoI/AAAAAAAAh-c/4wo8jxeefIM/s320/59793E7D-B617-486C-83FF-A91EA529C091_w640_r1_s.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>滕彪、李方平、肖国珍、刘巍等（网络图片）</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-TTe4lb3IsdA/UZJJGLsFeSI/AAAAAAAAh-M/DsKp-7U7I6k/s1600/%E5%94%90%E5%A4%A9%E6%98%8A%E5%A4%B4%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%97%E4%BC%A4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-TTe4lb3IsdA/UZJJGLsFeSI/AAAAAAAAh-M/DsKp-7U7I6k/s320/%E5%94%90%E5%A4%A9%E6%98%8A%E5%A4%B4%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%97%E4%BC%A4.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>唐天昊头部受伤（图片来源于网络）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-MNZEssOcibU/UZJJFTU4dlI/AAAAAAAAh-E/BricSk1B1zE/s1600/%E8%B5%84%E9%98%B3%E8%BF%8E%E6%8E%A5%E9%95%87%E4%BA%8C%E5%A8%A5%E6%B9%96%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"307\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-MNZEssOcibU/UZJJFTU4dlI/AAAAAAAAh-E/BricSk1B1zE/s320/%E8%B5%84%E9%98%B3%E8%BF%8E%E6%8E%A5%E9%95%87%E4%BA%8C%E5%A8%A5%E6%B9%96%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>资阳迎接镇二娥湖黑监狱</p>\n<p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,10435,9475,19196]}